      "desc:8": "§eThe End§r is entirely optional for §dNTM§r progression, but is home to §6Trixite§r, a unique extraterrestrial mineral that when processed can yield §6Plutonium§r, §6Cobalt§r and §6Niobium§r. The Niobium is of great interest as it is a great source for early §3Catalytic Cracking Towers§r.\n\nDue to only the main end island existing, Trixite Ore is a limited resourse.§r Trixite Crystals can also be obtained from an §6Asteroid Mining Ship§r, but it is not recommended.\n\n§dEt Futurum Requiem§r backports many modern end features, such as §eChorus Fruit§r and a respawnable §eEnder Dragon§r using §6End Crystals§r.\n\nThe §6Dragon Egg§r can also be used to create a Backpack which provides passive §eNight Vision§r, §eStrength 2§r and §eFire resistance§r, aswell as some §eRegeneration§r when on low health.\n\nEnderman farms can also be made using §3Fans§r to push the endermen into the killing zone.",
